where the sum runs over the N atoms of the 1 or more molecules in the asymmetric unit of the unit cell, and pi(r-ri) is the electron density at r due to an atom at ri. Substituting eqn (3) in eqn (Z), we obtain:

F(Q) = fl dr pi(r -ri) eiQ.’ s (da)
