Figure 2. (a) Average positional error as a function of the mean square atomic fluctuations for a restrained refinement of 25 pa data ((F)$z:). The error bars represent + 1 standard deviation, but for points beyond 2.0 A2 there are relatively few points per average. (b) Distribution of positional errors along the principal X-axes for a restrained refinement of the 25 ps data,
